{"id":305799,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/07/维权网-维权人士赵广军、朱萍萍被羁押30天后获取/","date":"2013-07-26T21:17:44Z","modified":"2013-07-26T21:17:44Z","title":"维权网 | 维权人士赵广军、朱萍萍被羁押30天后获取保候审（图）","content":"<div dir=\"ltr\">\n<div></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a></p>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员田静民报道）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">26</span><span>日下午</span><span>，在被北京市丰台区分局羁押</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">30</span><span>余天后，辽宁维权人士赵广军、上海维权人士朱萍萍相继以“取保候审”的方式获释。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">2013</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">18</span><span>日</span><span>，邓志波、张继新、赵广军、朱萍萍、吕动力等近</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">30</span><span>名各地维权人士被刑事拘留，罪名是“聚众扰乱公共秩序罪”，羁押在北京市西城区看守所。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">37</span><span>天后，邓志波、张继新、何祖华、王素娥等数十人于</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">25</span><span>日</span><span>以“取保候审</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">”</span><span>的方式“释放”。而取保候审通知书明确写着“证据不足，不批准逮捕”。可赵广军、吕动力、朱萍萍三人，当即却又被丰台分局以“寻衅滋事罪”再次刑拘，羁押在丰台区看守所。在被羁押</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">30</span><span>余天后，北京警方还是以“证据不足，不批准逮捕”、“取保候审”释放了赵广军、朱萍萍。两次刑事拘留共</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">68</span><span>天，他们没有犯罪事实，却被羁押在看守所；他们反腐维权，却被打击报复。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>得知赵广军获释的消息后，维权人士林明杰、王素娥、董奎红、沈丽秀、李风华等人纷纷前往丰台区看守所迎接。赵广军的身体非常虚弱，脸色苍白，走出看守所时都需要搀扶，但他仍是满脸笑容。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>然而，赵广军刚刚走出看守所，即被辽宁省盘锦市警方强制带回当地。赵广军表示如果被带回当地后无法与大家联系，就表明自己再次失去了人身自由。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>另据了解，陕西维权人士吕动力仍被羁押在丰台区看守所，其为了抗议非法关押，头部被殴打受伤，已经绝食多日；许乃来、何斌仍被羁押在朝阳区看守所；赵振甲仍被羁押在海淀区看守所；张福英被羁押在北京市第一看守所。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><span>因为呼吁、参与官员公示财产，关注、声援因要求官员公示财产被抓捕的丁家喜等人，各地在北京的上访维权代表有近</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">30</span><span>人因此被刑事拘留。各地上访维权人士希望外界在关注“十君子”的同时，也一同关注被羁押的上访维权代表。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n<table align=\"center\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-JIhfbuVz0r0/UfKKxNWKE4I/AAAAAAAAl5k/UYt3kP8RJKY/s1600/CI.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"240\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-JIhfbuVz0r0/UfKKxNWKE4I/AAAAAAAAl5k/UYt3kP8RJKY/s1600/CI.JPG\" width=\"320\" /></a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>连续被羁押68天的赵广军（左5）</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<div></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-HrCcZeZtsi4/UfKKvtGi0tI/AAAAAAAAl5g/b7BRSZ-luBc/s1600/CIMG0209.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"240\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-HrCcZeZtsi4/UfKKvtGi0tI/AAAAAAAAl5g/b7BRSZ-luBc/s320/CIMG0209.JPG\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-vdFk9QUQcSM/UfKK1n75MSI/AAAAAAAAl6A/JbinmYxUzEo/s1600/CIMG0214.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"240\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-vdFk9QUQcSM/UfKK1n75MSI/AAAAAAAAl6A/JbinmYxUzEo/s320/CIMG0214.JPG\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-MHFpfRBObkI/UfKKyEldCMI/AAAAAAAAl5s/MJ9LvY1wHJI/s1600/CIMG0210.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"240\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-MHFpfRBObkI/UfKKyEldCMI/AAAAAAAAl5s/MJ9LvY1wHJI/s320/CIMG0210.JPG\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-Ux6PziFYGbc/UfKKzkSyKII/AAAAAAAAl50/un7EXxZ9zgY/s1600/CIMG0213.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"240\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-Ux6PziFYGbc/UfKKzkSyKII/AAAAAAAAl50/un7EXxZ9zgY/s320/CIMG0213.JPG\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div></div>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n</div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=1